➜wolfram alpha已经启动
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=11355	22020
<a href="mailto:wmr89502270@gmail.com">wmr</a> 写道<i> "<a href="http://www.wolframalpha.com/">wolfram alpha</a>已经启动，它根本不是网络搜索引擎，只是一个返回资料库中有限数据的工具。假如没有现在索引网页的搜索引擎，它就是最好的了。比如搜索“<a href="http://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=china">China</a>”，anti-cnn就可以大做文章了。它最大的优点是强大的<a href="http://www.wolfram.com/products/mathematica/index.html">计算功能</a>，比如计算<a href="http://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=sqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1%2Bsqrt(1)1%2Bsqrt(1)1%2Bsqrt(1))))))))))))))))))))))">黄金分割值</a>，<a href="http://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=1%2B1%3Dx%2By%2Cx*y%3D1">计算方程</a>。<a href="http://www.wolframalpha.com/gallery.html">这里</a>有更多的功能展示。"</i>
